OL,3,CMan arrested after 5-year-old boy hit
OL,4,Cby van
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after a 5-year-
OL,7,Fold boy was hit by a van, suffering
OL,8,Finjuries which are 'thought to be
OL,9,Fserious'.
OL,11,FThe child was hit at the junction of
OL,12,FAldgate and Luton Road in Ellesmere
OL,13,FPort on Monday 1 September at around
OL,14,F4.30pm.
OL,16,FEmergency services, including an air
OL,17,Fambulance, were sent to the scene of
OL,18,Fthe incident. Aldgate was shut off by
OL,19,Fpolice at Sutton Way while cordons
OL,20,Fwere also put up near the Luton Road
OL,21,Fjunction.
