OL,3,CMan arrested after 5-year-old boy hit
OL,4,Cby van
OL,6,FCheshire Police then arrested the van
OL,7,Fdriver on suspicion of causing serious
OL,8,Finjury by dangerous driving, drink
OL,9,Fdriving, failing to co-operate with a
OL,10,Fpreliminary test, and driving while
OL,11,Funfit through drink.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Cheshire Constabulary
OL,14,Fsaid: "At 4.32pm on 1 September police
OL,15,Fwere called to a collision involving a
OL,16,Fvan and a pedestrian at the junction
OL,17,Fof Aldgate and Luton Road in Ellesmere
OL,18,FPort. The pedestrian, a 5-year-old
OL,19,Fboy, was taken to hospital with
OL,20,Finjuries which were thought to be
OL,21,Fserious.
