OL,6,F"The driver of the van was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing serious injury by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving, drink driving,
OL,9,Ffailing to co-operate with a
OL,10,Fpreliminary test and driving while
OL,11,Funfit through drink. Enquiries are
OL,12,Fcontinuing."
OL,14,FAnyone who witnessed the collision or
OL,15,Fhas dashcam footage, is urged to
OL,16,Fcontact Cheshire Police on 101 quoting
OL,17,FIML 2167547.
